      "title": "6 Sri Lankans take refuge in Dhanushkodi",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A total of 6 Sri Lankan Tamils, two boys, two men and two women, have taken shelter in the sand dunes near Dhanushkodi.",
        "According to Indian sources, a hovercraft belonging to the Indian Coast Guard is about to depart from Mandapam to rescue them."
      ],
